## COMPLIANCE — REMAINING GAPS

These require product/legal decisions, not just code:

| Item | Action Required |
|---|---|
| **Privacy Policy** | Draft and publish. Required for UK/EU public launch. |
| **Cookie Consent** | Add consent banner before setting `apex-token` cookie on first visit. |
| **Account Deletion (Right to Erasure)** | Build a "Delete my account" endpoint and UI that purges all user rows. |
| **Data Export (Right of Portability)** | Build a `GET /api/user/export` endpoint returning all user data as JSON. |
| **Data Retention Policy** | Define and document how long inactive accounts are kept. |
| **DPAs with Neon & Netlify** | Sign Data Processing Agreements with both vendors. |

