## FUTURE ENTERPRISE HARDENING

- Multi-factor authentication (TOTP)
- PostgreSQL Row-Level Security (RLS) as database-layer defence-in-depth
- JWT revocation store (blocklist table for forced session termination)
- Immutable audit log of authentication events and data mutations
- Automated dependency scanning (GitHub Dependabot + `npm audit` in CI)
- Content Security Policy nonces for strict inline-script blocking
- External penetration test before enterprise sales
- SOC 2 Type II / ISO 27001 preparation

